Choose the color theme in Webex Meetings and Webex Webinars
You can choose to view the meeting window in the standard Light Theme or in Dark Theme. Reduce eye strain by choosing the theme that works best with your lighting conditions.
Windows
Mac
Web App
iOS
Android
1
During the meeting, select the View menu.
2
Go to Themes and select your preferred theme. The options are Light Theme and Dark Theme. We'll remember your choice the next time that you use the Windows desktop app.

  This setting does not affect the color theme in your Meetings web app or mobile app.